00:01:30,170 --> 00:01:32,433
<i>[EPISODE 55]</i>

18
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:37,288
Xuanji.

19
00:01:37,288 --> 00:01:41,190
Xuanji! Xuanji.

20
00:01:45,779 --> 00:01:47,726
- Sifeng! <br> - Sifeng!

21
00:01:48,308 --> 00:01:49,619
Sifeng!

22
00:01:49,619 --> 00:01:52,019
- Sifeng! <br> - Sifeng! How are you feeling?

23
00:01:52,019 --> 00:01:53,820
Are you okay, Sifeng?

24
00:01:53,820 --> 00:01:55,511
Sifeng.

25
00:01:57,258 --> 00:01:59,031
Sifeng.

26
00:02:16,290 --> 00:02:21,588
<i>From now on, you are no longer the Devil Star, Devil Maleficent.</i>

27
00:02:21,588 --> 00:02:24,862
<i>You'll be Heaven's God of War.</i>

28
00:02:24,862 --> 00:02:29,459
<i>From tomorrow onward, you will be serving the heavens.</i>

29
00:02:29,459 --> 00:02:33,488
<i>You'll be the one to annihilate the Asuras</i>

30
00:02:33,488 --> 00:02:36,410
<i>and destroy the Demon Citadel.</i>

31
00:02:46,100 --> 00:02:48,628
It has been 1,000 years.

32
00:02:48,628 --> 00:02:52,556
Finally, this day has come.

33
00:02:57,740 --> 00:02:59,899
Greetings, Demon Lord.

34
00:02:59,899 --> 00:03:03,266
Congratulations for coming back to the three realms.

35
00:03:09,547 --> 00:03:11,621
Yuan Lang?

36
00:03:18,220 --> 00:03:20,399
I remember now.

37
00:03:20,399 --> 00:03:23,919
You were the Left and Right Lieutenant of King Asura.

38
00:03:24,605 --> 00:03:27,700
Looks like you still remember me.

39
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:33,217
I've been waiting for 1,000 years for you to be revived.

40
00:03:49,340 --> 00:03:52,267
Thank you for giving me a physical body again.

41
00:03:52,267 --> 00:03:55,100
I'm willing to fight the heavens with you

42
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:57,620
to finally seek revenge for Demon Citadel after 1,000 years.

43
00:03:57,620 --> 00:04:00,390
You can follow me then.

44
00:04:00,390 --> 00:04:02,219
Yuan Lang, you stupid bird.

45
00:04:02,219 --> 00:04:03,732
You are really a bad penny.

46
00:04:03,732 --> 00:04:06,108
He believes you because he has been sleeping for 1,000 years.

47
00:04:06,108 --> 00:04:09,073
Let me tell you. I won't let you escape today.

48
00:04:09,074 --> 00:04:12,980
Wait. I remember that the heavens have tortured you for 1,000 years, too.

49
00:04:12,980 --> 00:04:18,554
Don't you want to kill them together with me to avenge yourself?

50
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:27,330
I indeed detest those people from the heavens.

51
00:04:27,330 --> 00:04:30,559
I fought with them and stole their things 1,000 years ago.

52
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,699
So it's only normal that they locked me up,

53
00:04:32,699 --> 00:04:35,867
but now they even dared to hurt my Little Fox.

54
00:04:35,867 --> 00:04:37,675
Besides, I found out today that

55
00:04:37,675 --> 00:04:40,259
Bailing was so shameless to do that to you.

56
00:04:40,259 --> 00:04:43,618
You were once the person I admired the most,

57
00:04:43,618 --> 00:04:45,579
and Xuanji was my good friend.

58
00:04:45,579 --> 00:04:48,820
- So, I have to avenge all of you. <br> - Good.

59
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:50,859
Looks like I didn't misjudge you.

60
00:04:50,859 --> 00:04:54,370
But I have to kill this stupid bird today.

61
00:04:54,370 --> 00:04:57,003
I don't care what kind of grudge you have between you.

62
00:04:57,003 --> 00:05:00,830
Before we destroy the heavens, I don't want there to be an internal conflict.

63
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:04,299
After we seek our revenge, you can kill whoever you want.

64
00:05:04,299 --> 00:05:06,570
Just go ahead and do it.

65
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,840
Fine.

66
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:20,662
After all, that Bailing is more shameless than this zombie here.

67
00:05:20,662 --> 00:05:25,430
I'll kill Bailing first, and then I'll kill you.

68
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:31,610
If that's the case, come with me to Fenru City now.

69
00:05:31,610 --> 00:05:35,766
I want to give a present to the heavens.

70
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:56,619
King Bailing, Devil Maleficent has already destroyed Fenru City

71
00:05:56,619 --> 00:05:58,480
and broke the Core Fire.

72
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:03,250
He even went to the Demon Citadel to revive the Asuras army.

73
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:06,387
What about Shen Shu and Yu Lu?

74
00:06:16,460 --> 00:06:18,042
Please have mercy on us!

75
00:06:18,042 --> 00:06:20,373
Good-for-nothing.

76
00:06:20,373 --> 00:06:22,380
- King Bailing. <br> - Tell me.

77
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:23,939
What bad news is it this time?

78
00:06:23,939 --> 00:06:25,540
Devil Maleficent sent us a war declaration

79
00:06:25,540 --> 00:06:28,588
stating that he'll attack the heavens and drench it with blood.

80
00:06:31,368 --> 00:06:34,335
I never thought that my compassion back then

81
00:06:34,335 --> 00:06:37,946
would lead him act so arrogantly now.

82
00:06:37,946 --> 00:06:40,974
He wants to attack the heavens?

83
00:06:40,974 --> 00:06:43,268
Fine.

84
00:06:43,268 --> 00:06:45,587
Pass down my decree.

85
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:49,539
Put the whole heavens on high alert now.

86
00:06:49,539 --> 00:06:52,579
We won't give him an opportunity to take advantage of us!

87
00:06:52,579 --> 00:06:54,025
Yes, King Bailing.

88
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:01,824
Xuanji.

89
00:07:02,926 --> 00:07:04,673
Xuanji.

90
00:07:05,459 --> 00:07:08,599
Xuanji. Xuanji!

91
00:07:08,599 --> 00:07:10,159
- Sifeng! <br> - Sifeng!

92
00:07:10,159 --> 00:07:11,274
Where is Xuanji?

93
00:07:11,274 --> 00:07:14,359
Sifeng, Xuanji has already turned into Devil Maleficent now.

94
00:07:14,359 --> 00:07:16,499
- It's pointless to look for her! <br> - I want to look for her.

95
00:07:16,499 --> 00:07:18,219
Calm down!

96
00:07:18,219 --> 00:07:21,180
Even if she's Devil Maleficent, she's still Xuanji!

97
00:07:21,180 --> 00:07:24,220
Sifeng, Xuanji has become Devil Maleficent. She's gone.

98
00:07:24,220 --> 00:07:27,139
Devil Maleficent has summoned all demons to the Demon Citadel to greet him.

99
00:07:27,139 --> 00:07:30,177
He'll lead an attack towards the heavens and bring chaos to the three realms.

100
00:07:30,177 --> 00:07:31,659
When you were unconscious,

101
00:07:31,659 --> 00:07:34,059
demons were already acting so rampantly in the human realm.

102
00:07:34,059 --> 00:07:36,210
Now, no one dares to come out.

103
00:07:36,210 --> 00:07:38,681
The world is in a mess now.

104
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,860
No. Xuanji must still be alive.

105
00:07:42,860 --> 00:07:44,752
She's just controlled by Devil Maleficent for now.

106
00:07:44,752 --> 00:07:46,340
- I'll look for her tomorrow. <br> - No.

107
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:49,700
The majority of the demons are gathered at the Demon Citadel now. We can't be reckless.

108
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:51,820
I think we better discuss it with Master first.

109
00:07:51,820 --> 00:07:54,380
I'll go! You are mortals but I'm a demon.

110
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:57,819
Since it's a gathering of demons, all the more reason for me to go.

111
00:07:57,819 --> 00:07:59,100
Sifeng.

112
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:01,500
Sifeng, a lot of elders who didn't obey him

113
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:03,398
- have been killed. <br> - Yes.

114
00:08:03,398 --> 00:08:05,124
- I'm worried that you– <br> - No.

115
00:08:05,124 --> 00:08:09,100
Even if she's controlled by the Devil Star's soul, I'll find her.

116
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:12,731
The Devil Star's soul has been harboring hatred for 1,000 years in the Crystal Lamp.

117
00:08:12,731 --> 00:08:15,180
As soon as it combined with Xuanji's primordial spirit,

118
00:08:15,180 --> 00:08:17,831
I'm afraid that her mere 20 years of life

119
00:08:17,831 --> 00:08:21,439
is just nothing compared to Devil Maleficent's tens and thousands of years of memories.

120
00:08:21,439 --> 00:08:23,050
Yes.

121
00:08:23,050 --> 00:08:26,379
Bailing sealed up her six senses and took away all of her memories.

122
00:08:26,379 --> 00:08:29,627
He even transformed into Hao Chen and yet couldn't stop her from becoming him.

123
00:08:29,627 --> 00:08:32,340
From that, you can see how deep Devil Maleficent's hatred is.

124
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:34,767
Little Phoenix, you can't risk your life like this.

125
00:08:34,767 --> 00:08:37,019
Why are you so unconfident in Xuanji?

126
00:08:37,019 --> 00:08:39,539
Although Devil Maleficent's soul is controlling her now,

127
00:08:39,539 --> 00:08:42,026
it doesn't mean that she's completely gone.

128
00:08:42,026 --> 00:08:45,351
Devil Maleficent has hatred in his heart but Xuanji has love in her heart.

129
00:08:45,351 --> 00:08:49,299
I don't believe that someone can totally forget about the person they once loved.

130
00:08:49,299 --> 00:08:52,798
I believe that Xuanji is still alive, too. We can save her.

131
00:08:52,798 --> 00:08:57,639
It doesn't matter whether she's the God of War or the Devil Star.

132
00:08:57,650 --> 00:09:02,842
I will stop Devil Maleficent and bring back Xuanji.

133
00:09:02,842 --> 00:09:05,069
Please advise him against this.

134
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:10,264
Okay. If that's the case, I won't stop you anymore.

135
00:09:10,264 --> 00:09:12,168
You–

136
00:09:12,168 --> 00:09:14,140
But you have to remember this.

137
00:09:14,140 --> 00:09:17,140
The more people Devil Maleficent kills, the more demonic he will become.

138
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:19,315
If you want to get Xuanji back,

139
00:09:19,315 --> 00:09:22,420
you have to stop him from slaughtering people without restraint.

140
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,899
<i>Greetings, Demon Lord!</i>

141
00:09:32,899 --> 00:09:36,869
<i>Welcome back to the three realms!</i>

142
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:40,820
The heavens destroyed the Demon Citadel 1,000 years ago.

143
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:45,323
We demons were scattered across the realms and were suppressed and bullied.

144
00:09:45,323 --> 00:09:50,547
Now that I'm back, I'm going to stir up the three realms

145
00:09:50,547 --> 00:09:53,800
to restore the power and dignity of us demons.

146
00:09:54,376 --> 00:09:56,128
On the seventh day of the seventh month,

147
00:09:56,128 --> 00:10:00,559
I'll use the Fallen Bell to burst open heaven's gate and attack them.

148
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:03,195
Go and swear a blood oath with the Right Lieutenant later.

149
00:10:03,195 --> 00:10:06,427
Then, we'll slaughter everyone in the heavens together.

150
00:10:06,428 --> 00:10:09,580
<i>Attack the heavens! Slaughter everyone there!</i>

151
00:10:09,580 --> 00:10:12,430
<i>Restore the power of demons again!</i>

152
00:10:13,244 --> 00:10:17,659
This is Demon Lord's first order and someone is already defying it.

153
00:10:17,659 --> 00:10:20,108
Well done.

154
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:26,810
My clan has little power. The spirit is willing, but the flesh is weak.

155
00:10:26,810 --> 00:10:29,132
I hope that...

156
00:10:38,187 --> 00:10:42,614
Since you are of no help, why should I keep you?

157
00:10:43,420 --> 00:10:47,354
Demon Lord, you said that we've been suppressed and bullied for 1,000 years.

158
00:10:47,354 --> 00:10:49,611
You want to lead us to fight against the heavens.

159
00:10:49,611 --> 00:10:52,355
We came here because we respect you.

160
00:10:52,355 --> 00:10:54,739
But not every clan is good at combat.

161
00:10:54,739 --> 00:10:56,339
How can you just kill us like that?

162
00:10:56,339 --> 00:10:57,803
Insolent!

163
00:10:57,803 --> 00:11:00,886
He was just gone for 1,000 years and now, even a mere Green Sparrow

164
00:11:00,886 --> 00:11:03,445
is teaching him how to lead?

165
00:11:03,445 --> 00:11:06,979
You are humiliating us just like how the heavens treat us.

166
00:11:06,979 --> 00:11:08,798
Goodbye!

167
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:18,010
<i>Calm down, Demon Lord.</i>

168
00:11:18,010 --> 00:11:23,530
The heavens annihilated us Asuras and drove away the rest of your demons.

169
00:11:23,530 --> 00:11:28,059
All of you have been hiding in fear for more than 1,000 years.

170
00:11:28,059 --> 00:11:32,210
At first, I thought that all of you would look forward to seeking revenge.

171
00:11:32,210 --> 00:11:34,322
But I never thought that this insult of 1,000 years

172
00:11:34,322 --> 00:11:39,230
would turn you into mellow and obedient cowards.

173
00:11:39,230 --> 00:11:40,739
As demons,

174
00:11:40,739 --> 00:11:45,296
are you really going to just hide in the human realm and be slaughtered?

175
00:11:45,296 --> 00:11:49,403
I won't accept this kind of humiliation,

176
00:11:49,403 --> 00:11:52,614
and it'll be the same for every demon clan!

177
00:11:52,614 --> 00:11:55,137
I don't care if you want to swear the blood oath or not.

178
00:11:55,137 --> 00:11:57,900
From today onward, we are no longer separated by clans.

179
00:11:57,900 --> 00:11:59,899
All of you will obey me.

180
00:11:59,899 --> 00:12:02,193
We'll gather here on the seventh day of the seventh month.

181
00:12:02,193 --> 00:12:05,196
This is an order, not a discussion.

182
00:12:05,196 --> 00:12:07,296
Those who disobey me

183
00:12:07,296 --> 00:12:10,050
will be killed without mercy.

184
00:12:10,050 --> 00:12:11,787
<i>Yes, Demon Lord!</i>

185
00:12:16,140 --> 00:12:18,103
You are dismissed.

186
00:12:20,180 --> 00:12:22,368
Sifeng?

187
00:12:22,368 --> 00:12:24,525
Yu Sifeng.

188
00:12:24,525 --> 00:12:26,514
It's you?

189
00:12:26,514 --> 00:12:29,337
12 Feathers Rose Gold Bird?

190
00:12:38,736 --> 00:12:40,962
I know that Xuanji's consciousness is still there.

191
00:12:40,962 --> 00:12:43,147
She won't let you commit the sin of murder.

192
00:12:43,147 --> 00:12:45,033
Let her out!

193
00:12:45,860 --> 00:12:47,602
<i>Sifeng.</i>

194
00:12:47,602 --> 00:12:51,146
<i>Sifeng! Sifeng!</i>

195
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:54,123
<i>Sifeng!</i>

196
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:04,125
<i>Sifeng!</i>

197
00:13:04,125 --> 00:13:08,538
Xuanji, you became Devil Maleficent to save me.

198
00:13:09,620 --> 00:13:13,049
Have you forgotten about me now that you've become Devil Maleficent?

199
00:13:13,049 --> 00:13:14,749
<i>Sifeng!</i>

200
00:13:16,820 --> 00:13:19,763
Devil Maleficent, let me out!

201
00:13:19,763 --> 00:13:22,574
<i>Let me out!</i>

202
00:13:22,574 --> 00:13:26,822
Chu Xuanji is just the image of my primordial spirit.

203
00:13:26,822 --> 00:13:31,498
Since I'm already back, she is gone now.

204
00:13:31,498 --> 00:13:37,402
Stop mentioning this lowly mortal's name again and again in front of me.

205
00:13:38,421 --> 00:13:40,986
Xuanji will not be gone.

206
00:13:40,986 --> 00:13:43,383
I'm sure that she's still here.

207
00:13:43,383 --> 00:13:45,372
She was controlled

208
00:13:45,372 --> 00:13:48,283
by your soul because she wanted to save me.

209
00:13:48,283 --> 00:13:51,850
Although she was once part of your primordial spirit,

210
00:13:51,850 --> 00:13:54,580
she has gone through 1,000 years with 10 reincarnations.

211
00:13:54,580 --> 00:13:56,692
She's her own person now.

212
00:13:56,692 --> 00:13:59,100
She's not Devil Maleficent.

213
00:13:59,100 --> 00:14:01,030
Xuanji,

214
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:03,668
I know that you are inside him. Right?

215
00:14:05,796 --> 00:14:08,550
<i>Devil Maleficent, let me out!</i>

216
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:10,819
So what if she's here?

217
00:14:10,819 --> 00:14:12,914
So what if she's not?

218
00:14:12,914 --> 00:14:17,390
She's just a small portion in this long life of mine.

219
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:20,259
Among my tens and thousands of years of memories,

220
00:14:20,259 --> 00:14:23,469
hers is just a drop of water in the ocean.

221
00:14:23,469 --> 00:14:28,217
Do you think she can control me? Dream on.

222
00:14:28,860 --> 00:14:32,379
Since you once risked your life to protect my primordial spirit,

223
00:14:32,379 --> 00:14:34,590
I'll not kill you.

224
00:14:34,590 --> 00:14:36,687
Get lost now.

225
00:14:36,687 --> 00:14:40,699
I promised Xuanji that I would bring her back.

226
00:14:40,699 --> 00:14:43,419
I won't leave until she appears!

227
00:14:43,419 --> 00:14:46,876
Sifeng, wake up, you dummy.

228
00:14:46,876 --> 00:14:48,320
She's not Xuanji now.

229
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,450
I believe in Xuanji!

230
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:52,773
She is not the Devil Star.

231
00:14:54,544 --> 00:14:57,553
And she doesn't want to be Devil Star.

232
00:14:57,553 --> 00:15:00,829
Aren't you afraid that I'll kill you?

233
00:15:02,241 --> 00:15:04,161
You won't,

234
00:15:04,161 --> 00:15:08,290
because Xuanji won't allow you to kill me.

235
00:15:08,290 --> 00:15:11,819
I already said that she's just a part of my primordial spirit.

236
00:15:11,819 --> 00:15:14,266
Do you think that you can stop me?

237
00:15:14,266 --> 00:15:16,433
You tried so hard to lock Xuanji up

238
00:15:16,433 --> 00:15:20,310
and used your power to take the form of Devil Maleficent

239
00:15:20,310 --> 00:15:22,219
because you are afraid.

240
00:15:22,219 --> 00:15:24,379
You are afraid that you can't control her.

241
00:15:24,379 --> 00:15:30,730
