00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:17,506
Little Fox is dead.

497
00:35:18,348 --> 00:35:21,201
I promised her that I wouldn't fight anymore.

498
00:35:22,324 --> 00:35:24,749
So I came here to save you.

499
00:35:25,820 --> 00:35:27,644
Let's go.

500
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:31,635
Both of you are just going to leave without goodbyes?

501
00:35:31,635 --> 00:35:34,820
Such disrespect for the Demon Lord.

502
00:35:34,820 --> 00:35:38,059
Demon Lord, I've already said that Yu Sifeng was going to rebel.

503
00:35:38,059 --> 00:35:41,530
Now, looks like Wu Zhiqi wants to leave, too.

504
00:35:41,530 --> 00:35:43,968
Both of them are traitors.

505
00:35:43,968 --> 00:35:48,219
Wu Zhiqi, I respected you 1,000 years ago.

506
00:35:48,219 --> 00:35:52,260
And now you are the only one who doesn't need to address me as Demon Lord.

507
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:54,455
I treated you well.

508
00:35:54,455 --> 00:35:57,667
Why are you leaving me now that we are defeated?

509
00:35:57,667 --> 00:36:00,518
Is it just like what Yuan Lang said?

510
00:36:00,518 --> 00:36:03,070
Are you going to betray me?

511
00:36:04,020 --> 00:36:07,930
I don't know what betrayal means.

512
00:36:07,930 --> 00:36:11,750
Just now, Little Fox died saving me from that battle.

513
00:36:11,750 --> 00:36:15,061
I've already promised her not to fight anymore.

514
00:36:15,061 --> 00:36:17,970
I'm going to bring her home and bury her demonic core.

515
00:36:18,838 --> 00:36:23,887
Devil Maleficent, I think I've repaid you enough for

516
00:36:23,887 --> 00:36:27,102
speaking up for me to King Asura back then.

517
00:36:27,102 --> 00:36:30,835
From now on, I'm no longer in debt to you.

518
00:36:30,835 --> 00:36:35,639
Old Wu, you want to bargain with the Demon Lord?

519
00:36:35,639 --> 00:36:38,103
Aren't you too arrogant?

520
00:36:38,103 --> 00:36:40,303
What did you say?

521
00:36:41,339 --> 00:36:44,454
I misunderstood you then.

522
00:36:44,454 --> 00:36:48,411
Being sentimental and loyal are your best qualities.

523
00:36:48,411 --> 00:36:51,859
I wasn't expecting you to pay me back when I spoke up for you back then.

524
00:36:51,859 --> 00:36:55,522
Since you want to leave now, I won't force you to stay.

525
00:36:55,522 --> 00:36:57,398
You can leave,

526
00:36:57,398 --> 00:37:00,170
but Yu Sifeng has to stay.

527
00:37:02,740 --> 00:37:05,852
Yu Sifeng, you put down an order to foil our military plan.

528
00:37:05,852 --> 00:37:07,419
That's a fatal crime.

529
00:37:07,419 --> 00:37:10,010
Do you have anything to say for yourself?

530
00:37:10,010 --> 00:37:13,019
Devil Maleficent, you have Xuanji's memories inside you.

531
00:37:13,019 --> 00:37:16,355
I did it so that you wouldn't commit even more sins of murder

532
00:37:16,355 --> 00:37:19,390
and suffer in the future.

533
00:37:19,390 --> 00:37:23,418
I can kill you. I can let you go, too.

534
00:37:23,418 --> 00:37:25,850
Xuanji is making you do it, right?

535
00:37:25,850 --> 00:37:27,609
Don't think too much.

536
00:37:27,609 --> 00:37:33,499
For me, Chu Xuanji is just a fragment in my mind. She's powerless,

537
00:37:33,499 --> 00:37:38,010
but you are quite interesting.

538
00:37:38,010 --> 00:37:41,627
How about this? I know that you are the leader of the Rose Gold Birds.

539
00:37:41,627 --> 00:37:43,499
If you do something for me,

540
00:37:43,499 --> 00:37:47,950
I'll forgive you for the crimes that you've committed.

541
00:37:47,950 --> 00:37:49,300
What is it?

542
00:37:49,300 --> 00:37:52,085
Find the Rose Gold Birds. Order them to burn their demonic cores

543
00:37:52,085 --> 00:37:54,688
and carry my army over the Sea of Life and Death.

544
00:37:54,688 --> 00:37:56,436
Burn their demonic cores?

545
00:37:56,436 --> 00:38:01,391
You'll destroy their cultivations and turn them into cripples.

546
00:38:01,391 --> 00:38:05,570
It's their honor to be able to die for the Demon Lord.

547
00:38:05,570 --> 00:38:08,986
Yu Sifeng, just agree to it.

548
00:38:10,507 --> 00:38:14,950
Unfortunately, I'm already not their leader since a few years back.

549
00:38:14,950 --> 00:38:17,423
So, I don't know where they are.

550
00:38:17,423 --> 00:38:21,010
But Yuan Lang is the Rose Gold Bird with the most advanced cultivation.

551
00:38:21,010 --> 00:38:26,130
With his power, he can fly through that sea seven to eight times without a problem.

552
00:38:26,130 --> 00:38:30,378
You can bestow to him this honor of burning his demonic core instead.

553
00:38:30,378 --> 00:38:35,019
Yu Sifeng, I'm giving you a chance because I think that you are very amusing.

554
00:38:35,019 --> 00:38:37,470
Don't be so imperious.

555
00:38:38,243 --> 00:38:42,450
Since you won't tell me about the Rose Gold Bird's whereabouts,

556
00:38:42,450 --> 00:38:45,317
I'll have to kill you.

557
00:38:45,317 --> 00:38:47,019
I really don't know.

558
00:38:47,019 --> 00:38:49,979
If you don't believe me, just kill me then.

559
00:38:49,979 --> 00:38:52,028
Okay.

560
00:38:55,740 --> 00:38:57,099
Eldest Brother Wu.

561
00:38:57,099 --> 00:39:01,602
Devil Maleficent, Sifeng is my friend and my savior.

562
00:39:01,602 --> 00:39:06,420
If you want to kill him, I'll help him even if it'll cost me my life.

563
00:39:06,420 --> 00:39:08,041
Eldest Brother Wu.

564
00:39:09,252 --> 00:39:12,259
Demon Lord, they are obviously trying to revolt against you.

565
00:39:12,259 --> 00:39:14,995
Just kill them to prevent any future troubles.

566
00:39:14,995 --> 00:39:17,430
Interesting.

567
00:39:19,620 --> 00:39:23,899
I haven't seen such loyalty in a friendship for a long time.

568
00:39:23,899 --> 00:39:26,357
It'll be a pity if I kill you both.

569
00:39:26,357 --> 00:39:30,969
But if I just pardon Yu Sifeng like this, others will think that I'm unfair.

570
00:39:30,969 --> 00:39:33,740
What a dilemma.

571
00:39:33,740 --> 00:39:38,093
How about this. If the two of you can withstand three attacks from me,

572
00:39:38,093 --> 00:39:42,259
I'll consider that Yu Sifeng has paid for his crime.

573
00:39:42,259 --> 00:39:44,531
But if you die,

574
00:39:44,531 --> 00:39:48,342
you can only blame yourself for not being powerful enough.

575
00:39:48,342 --> 00:39:52,660
Demon Lord, Rose Gold Bird is useful to us. We can't let Yu Sifeng go.

576
00:39:52,660 --> 00:39:56,410
I've already made up my mind. No need to say anything else.

577
00:39:59,260 --> 00:40:00,617
Eldest Brother Wu!

578
00:40:04,677 --> 00:40:06,347
Sifeng!

579
00:40:07,253 --> 00:40:09,547
Sifeng, how are you?

580
00:40:09,547 --> 00:40:11,716
Don't worry. I'm fine.

581
00:40:20,340 --> 00:40:23,739
You are using the Solar Palm from the Golden Crow Tactic to attack yourself

582
00:40:23,739 --> 00:40:26,970
