583
00:40:26,970 --> 00:40:29,288
Interesting.

584
00:40:29,288 --> 00:40:32,232
But both of you are seriously injured right now.

585
00:40:32,232 --> 00:40:36,570
The third one, Soul Breaker, will attack your heart and soul. It's very dangerous.

586
00:40:36,570 --> 00:40:38,800
You still want to try it?

587
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:40,601
Sure.

588
00:40:45,060 --> 00:40:50,387
If we are to die here together today, I'll be content with that!

589
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:57,508
